Quickstrike:





Quickstrike bolted from the base, mad as ever. He was mad that he was 
kept in the dark about these new situations. He bolted over KitKat 
and her gang, digging the ridged bottom edges of his feet into the 
ground as he stopped. 

"What in tarnation is goin' on?" he snapped.
